<font color="#FF0000">TEACHING ABOUT VIETNAM</font><br>
<tt>Thu Feb 20 16:25:10 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
First time on this site. Congratulations to all who teach and who want tolearn. I offer a course at Colorado State on The Vietnam War in Fiction, teaching selected novels by internal chronology and providing context as we move from Greene's QUIET AMERICAN (set in 1952) to Bobbie Ann Mason's IN COUNTRY (set in 1984. Books atr becomg hard to find, though, so I've had to publish some under my own imprint.<br><br>
I served in Vietnam/Laos/Laos/Thailand and have written a few books about the war myself. Keep going, everyone.
